id: pm-xm7c
title: "CLI+MCP surface for atomic bulk item mutations: JSON mutation batch on stdin over commitItemMutations"
description: ""
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[3]: cli,multi-agent,sdk-first
created_at: "2026-07-19T14:43:37.560Z"
